  "text": "DNA was extracted from swab heads using the MP Bio FastDNA Spin Kit for Soil (http://www.mpbio.com). A single sample was examined for each subject. Blank controls with no sample added were taken from each DNA extraction kit to test for contamination [CITATION_1] .",
